¶ ⦊
  ‖ \ssection{Why} ⦉
⦉

¶ ⦊
  ‖ Suppose we are going to make a several measurements.
    ‖ We associate to each element of a finite set a number. ⦉

    ‖ If the measurements we make are divided into proportions
      according to a distribution, if we make all the
      measurements and then average the results what do we expect
      to get.
